The paper deals with computer vision and graphics, specifically in the area of video re-animation and transfer. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves generative neural networks, which falls under cs.GR (Graphics). Additionally, the paper involves video processing and manipulation, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of adversarial training suggests a focus on machine learning, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves the transfer of facial expressions and eye gaze, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
